    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "PROCESS可以是多种类型，比如Data Action、Genesys Function或者Web Service。你在这个节点上方加个Note说明一下，用<br换行列出这几种可能。另外整个图要用redux-color主题，经典外观。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "PROCESS",
        "Note",
        "config theme",
        "look"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把基础结构搭出来：CALLER发起呼叫到FLOW，FLOW激活后调用PROCESS。PROCESS返回结果给FLOW，最后FLOW再返回来电者。流程是同步的，所以用实线箭头加加号表示激活。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CALLER",
        "FLOW",
        "PROCESS",
        "activate",
        "deactivate"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，中间这个等待环节需要突出一下。FinTech的LedgerService调用通常有延迟，我想用高亮区域把这段WAITING TIME LOST标出来，背景色用FinTech_LedgerService这个rgba值。",
      "elements_involved": [
