    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下：rect范围覆盖从CALLER到FLOW，里面放Note写WAITING TIME LOST，对吗？还有PROCESS返回结果到FLOW，这条线是用虚线还是实线？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "rect",
