      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，rect跨CALLER和FLOW。PROCESS返回用三条虚线，表示异步回调结果；最后FLOW到CALLER的continue journey用双虚线，然后两边都deactivate。标题定为SYNCHRONOUS GENESYS WORKFLOW。",
